node.text:
The most affected region by Coronavirus in Italy 💔 Lombardia is located in the center of Italy and Europe. Home to a variety of industries such as agriculture, manufacturing, fashion and eco-tourism. ⠀

The breathtaking landscape of Lombardy is a mixture of hills, mountains, lakes and plains. Its Alpine area is very popular in winter by skiers. Nature lovers are greeted by beautiful shoreline along the great Lombard lakes: Lake Garda, Lake Como, Lake Maggiore and Lake Iseo. ⠀

Stay strong Italy! 💚🤍❤️ #ForzaItalia

Video by @idressitalian ⠀

Always #wondermore

Visit: https://wonderlustcollective.co

node.text:
⠀
How incredible is this waterfall? 😱💦

As the second most powerful waterfall in Europe and most voluminous waterfall in Iceland, Dettifoss has a reputation to uphold. Measuring 144 ft or 45 meters high and 100 meters wide, Dettifoss draws huge crowds each year and is one of the sites which make up the famous Diamond Circle of North Iceland - Húsavík, Ábyrgi Canyon, Lake Mývatn, and Dettifoss waterfall.

Have you ever been to Iceland? 

🎥 by @world.from.my.eyes 

📍Vatnajökull, Iceland 

#wondermore

node.text:
⠀
TETON CABIN STAY GIVEAWAY!! ⛰🏠

We’ve teamed up with @maisontetonia to give one lucky winner a 3 night stay at their amazing western getaway that’s right outside Teton and Yellowstone National Parks!

To Enter:
1) Follow @maisontetonia + @wonderlustcollective 
2) Like & Save this post
3) Tag friends in separate comments
1 Comment = 1 Entry. Unlimited Entries
**BONUS** Share this Post in your Story and Tag Us

Entries close Thursday 09/23 at midnight pst. Winner will be drawn Friday 09/24 at 3 pm pst and announced via @wonderlustcollective.

Prize must be claimed within one year and winner must have a valid Airbnb account!
*
Travel to and from location is not provided. 
-
We will never DM you any links to claim prize!
-
Good luck!! ❤️
-
(This giveaway is not sponsored by Instagram)
